\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e4a822a2a4e65f9f0200f3232d42eb15b75f27","tid":2419443,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"24歲男學生雷震霆涉於前年11月12日在荃灣沙咀道「comebuy」店外管有一把玻璃鎚，被控一項管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產罪。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wdv9NcO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWdv9NcO.jpg&h=54426ef3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}